<tree text="Kath&#x101;vatthu-a&#x1E6D;&#x1E6D;hakath&#x101;" target="text">
  <text>
    <gatha type="1">Nisinno  devalokasmiṃ, devasaṅghapurakkhato;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Sadevakassa lokassa, satthā appaṭipuggalo.</gatha>
    <gatha type="1">Sabbapaññattikusalo, paññattiparidīpanaṃ;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Vatvā puggalapaññattiṃ, loke uttamapuggalo.</gatha>
    <gatha type="1">Yaṃ puggalakathādīnaṃ, kathānaṃ vatthubhāvato;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Kathāvatthuppakaraṇaṃ, saṅkhepena adesayī.</gatha>
    <gatha type="1">Mātikāṭhapaneneva , ṭhapitassa surālaye;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Tassa moggaliputtena, vibhattassa mahītale.</gatha>
    <gatha type="1">Idāni yasmā sampatto, atthasaṃvaṇṇanākkamo;</gatha>
    <gatha type="last">Tasmā naṃ vaṇṇayissāmi, taṃ suṇātha samāhitāti.</gatha>
  </text>
</tree>
